### ===================================================
### General & System endpoints
### ===================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health check (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Health check with language
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Accept-Language: en

### Discovery (no auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/discovery

### Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ---------------------------------------------------
### Authenticated endpoints
### ---------------------------------------------------

### Login first
# @name loginRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Central health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/central
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Get sync status
GET {{baseUrl}}/sync/status
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Get system settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}

### Update system settings (admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enable_read_only_mode": false
}
